  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/0301baea245175b4d499362ab12608aa.avif?t=1716557966\" width=500 height=300 /></span><br><br>You Are Liam: Shadow Memories is a first-person psychological horror game where you will come to terms with who you really are. You are Liam.<br><br>You (Liam) have done some things you're not very proud of. Now you must enter your own mind to come to terms with the things you've done. Loop around rooms, solve puzzles, and hide from different monsters as you uncover your own truth. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/297d4e85b811c8584ef79e4211889b58.avif?t=1716557966\" width=500 height=300 /></span><br><br>- Looping around rooms in order to solve puzzles & progress.<br>- Multiple different monsters to hide and run away from throughout the game.<br>- A variety of puzzles to solve.<br>- Each monster has 10 potential jumpscares.<br>- A leaning mechanic to get a better look from behind a wall without exposing yourself.<br>- Secrets and clues to help uncover Liam's story.<br>- Pick up eyes to see what the monsters see.<br>- Spooks and scares.<br>- Not every door is safe. You'll need to listen carefully for breathing before opening them.<br>- Multiple endings.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/f98a47638e86302ecec79948d52aa76c.poster.avif?t=1716557966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/f98a47638e86302ecec79948d52aa76c.webm?t=1716557966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/f98a47638e86302ecec79948d52aa76c.mp4?t=1716557966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/5927aea433975302d560d860ab195a4f.poster.avif?t=1716557966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/5927aea433975302d560d860ab195a4f.webm?t=1716557966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/5927aea433975302d560d860ab195a4f.mp4?t=1716557966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/901cbdac893e0b4ba4e523748c85827b.poster.avif?t=1716557966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/901cbdac893e0b4ba4e523748c85827b.webm?t=1716557966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/901cbdac893e0b4ba4e523748c85827b.mp4?t=1716557966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/0301baea245175b4d499362ab12608aa.avif?t=1716557966\" width=500 height=300 /></span><br><br>You Are Liam: Shadow Memories is a first-person psychological horror game where you will come to terms with who you really are. You are Liam.<br><br>You (Liam) have done some things you're not very proud of. Now you must enter your own mind to come to terms with the things you've done. Loop around rooms, solve puzzles, and hide from different monsters as you uncover your own truth. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/297d4e85b811c8584ef79e4211889b58.avif?t=1716557966\" width=500 height=300 /></span><br><br>- Looping around rooms in order to solve puzzles & progress.<br>- Multiple different monsters to hide and run away from throughout the game.<br>- A variety of puzzles to solve.<br>- Each monster has 10 potential jumpscares.<br>- A leaning mechanic to get a better look from behind a wall without exposing yourself.<br>- Secrets and clues to help uncover Liam's story.<br>- Pick up eyes to see what the monsters see.<br>- Spooks and scares.<br>- Not every door is safe. You'll need to listen carefully for breathing before opening them.<br>- Multiple endings.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/f98a47638e86302ecec79948d52aa76c.poster.avif?t=1716557966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/f98a47638e86302ecec79948d52aa76c.webm?t=1716557966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/f98a47638e86302ecec79948d52aa76c.mp4?t=1716557966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/5927aea433975302d560d860ab195a4f.poster.avif?t=1716557966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/5927aea433975302d560d860ab195a4f.webm?t=1716557966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/5927aea433975302d560d860ab195a4f.mp4?t=1716557966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/901cbdac893e0b4ba4e523748c85827b.poster.avif?t=1716557966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/901cbdac893e0b4ba4e523748c85827b.webm?t=1716557966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626680/extras/901cbdac893e0b4ba4e523748c85827b.mp4?t=1716557966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
